    <div class="faq-a" id="priority-order-for-contacts-the-author-of-the-link"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Link reclamation is the process of finding and recovering backlinks that once pointed to your site but no longer do. This includes broken backlinks, unlinked brand mentions, lost backlinks, and incorrect links. It is one of the highest-ROI link building tactics because you are reaching out to sites that already know and trust your brand.</p></div></div>
