    <div class="faq-a" id="how-do-i-prevent-link-loss-in-the-first-place"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Prevent link loss with these practices: Never delete pages without 301 redirects. Maintain consistent URL structures during redesigns. Monitor your backlink profile monthly. Set up Google Alerts for brand mentions. Publish consistently so new links outpace lost links. Use a redirect plugin or server-level redirects for all URL changes. For more prevention tactics, see our guide on <a href="/blog/fix-broken-links/">fixing broken links</a> before they become reclamation targets.</p></div></div>
