<p>Link reclamation is not a hack. It is maintenance. The best SEOs treat it as a monthly practice, not a one-time project. Every reclaimed link restores authority you already earned. Every prevented loss protects future rankings.</p>
<p>Start with one research session this week. Export your lost backlinks from Ahrefs. Find 10 high-priority opportunities. Send 5 personalized emails. Track your results. Build the habit. If you want links without the manual outreach, explore how <a href="/blog/haro-link-building/">HARO link building</a> can earn you mentions from journalists.</p>
<p>The sites that rank in 2026 are not the sites with the most links. They are the sites that protect the links they have while building new ones. Reclamation is how you protect what you have earned.</p>
